{"tid":2264060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街頭派防疫物資 三市民被票控違限聚令今提堂","createTime":"2020-10-30T10:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T12:53:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"79f74241f0d527db12878a205007a915d9774470","tid":2264060,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"兩名市民稱今年4月於旺角擺街站派發防疫物資，突遭40多名警員包圍並票控違反四人禁聚令，其間在場的一名14歲女童亦同遭檢控。三人今於九龍城法院提堂，同被票控一項受禁群組聚集罪，三人要求暫緩答辯，等候法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指兩人於今年4月19日在旺角西洋菜街近奶路臣街違反受禁群組限制，兩人要求暫緩答辯。同案14歲女童則於法院的少年法庭提訊，三人的傳票均獲准押後至12月18日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/T7D7HDKRPFFVPFRVX3OSEPHME4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FT7D7HDKRPFFVPFRVX3OSEPHME4%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdtRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=8d2bdbc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FT7D7HDKRPFFVPFRVX3OSEPHME4%2F&h=d6c87dc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/T7D7HDKRPFFVPFRVX3OSEPHME4/</a>"},{"pid":"61a6335b1aab197cf6c1a72b1142470f7476ed95","tid":2264060,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd0292610aa0695b7a10604b666fab9e660192a","tid":2264060,"uid":39872,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"打壓人權又一例證<br />\n應納入制裁罪證"},{"pid":"0294fd75d68edd9b3c86da50f328e4e967add682","tid":2264060,"uid":226955,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:45:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">宜家皇軍唔高興</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f0b5c60d177d06044173d74259b24dfd962